SOLARIS-SCREENSHOT TESTS
-----------
Tests that verify "Take Screenshot" functionality.

Safety
------
These tests are non-destructive and safe to run.

Configuration
-------------
No configuration is needed

Version
-------
Tests were updated for Solaris11 and its update release

Available Testsuites
--------------------

* take screenshot
  Tests that take and verify screen shots
  - Grab Desktop with effects on/off
    Takes a screen shot of the entire desktop with effects on/off
  - Grab Window with effects on/off
    Takes a screen shot of the current window after a delay with 
    effects on/off
  - Grab Area
    Takes a screen shot of a small area of the screen
